From bb88c3d746958985c0d12c94b5a2940af5ab132f Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: =?UTF-8?q?G=CE=9BB?= <Gab@CosmoLabs.org>
Date: Sun, 19 Apr 2026 15:10:30 -0300
Subject: [PATCH 1/2] feat(mcp): add MCP server for Claude Desktop integration
 (ROAD-032)

Implements `smoke mcp` subcommand exposing 7 tools over stdio:

- smoke_run: execute tests with tag/timeout/fail-fast options
- smoke_init: auto-detect project and generate .smoke.yaml
- smoke_validate: check config validity without running tests
- smoke_list: enumerate tests with assertions and tags
- smoke_discover: find .smoke.yaml files in directory tree
- smoke_explain: document all 29 assertion types with examples
- smoke_generate_test: create single-test YAML snippets

Uses mark3labs/mcp-go v0.48.0 (only new dependency). Includes fix
suggestion engine that maps failure patterns to actionable remediation
for all assertion types.

9 new files, ~1300 LOC, 22 tests passing.
